{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_08_01_short",
  "title": "兵藤雫 1話 野生に目覚めたアイドル (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニピの無人島ロケより少し前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A little before Sunny Peace's deserted island shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "雫、無人島ロケの日が迫ってるけど、準備は順調か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ the deserted island shoot is approaching. Are preparations going smoothly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2666664958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "準備は……バッチリ。議論に議論を重ねて\nそれぞれ必要なものを選んだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Preparations are… perfect. After much discussion and deliberation‚\nwe each chose what we needed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.3333331625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、みんなで力を合わせて頑張ってるんだな\nそれは何よりだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ everyone's working together and doing their best.\nThat's good above all‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6333331625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……？\nなんだか浮かない顔……どうかしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…?\nYou look a bit down… what's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.1999998291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今回はサニピのみんなが熱望したから\nオファーを受けたが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time everyone in Sunny Peace was eager for it‚\nso I accepted the offer‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5999988119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "脱出成功率1パーセントなんて数字を聞くと\nどうしても心配してしまうんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I hear numbers like a 1 percent escape success rate‚\nI can't help but worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.1999988119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8000009496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "そんな風に心配してくれる人がいるから……\n私達も、無茶はしないようにしようって思える",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because there's someone who worries about us like that…\nIt makes us feel like we shouldn't do anything reckless either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3999998291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはほんとに心強い……\nさすがは星見プロの……お父さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san is really reassuring…\nAs expected of Hoshimi Pro's… father?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7999998291,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}